---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Childcare Employee Benefits | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Learn how offering the right employee benefits can improve retention and ROI for your childcare business."
>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
        <!-- 1. OWNERSHIP FRAMING -->
        <section class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                YOUR employee retention
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Building a loyal team isn't just about luck—it's about creating
                an environment where staff feel valued and secure through
                strategic benefits.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. FACTORS THAT AFFECT OUTCOME -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                What Affects Your Retention ROI
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                The return on investment for employee benefits varies widely
                based on your local market rates, the specific mix of benefits
                you offer, and the long-term cost of turnover in your area.
                Every center's financial capacity and staff demographics create
                a unique landscape for what works best.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. WHY GENERIC ADVICE FAILS -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Why Online Advice Often Conflicts
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Generic articles often suggest expensive packages that don't
                match the reality of a small to mid-sized childcare business.
                Your strategy needs to be tailored to your specific budget and
                the actual needs of your team, not a one-size-fits-all corporate
                playbook.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. CTA TO CALCULATOR -->
        <section
            class="text-center py-12 px-8 glass-panel rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                See How Much YOU Could Make in Your State
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Get your personalized income estimate based on your state's
                regulations to see what budget you have for benefits.
            </p>
            <a
                href="/tools/income-builder"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 shadow-lg transition-all"
            >
                Use the Free Calculator →
            </a>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
